OL,3,CWarning issued after fire caused by
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes in lorry
OL,6,FA Welsh fire service has issued a
OL,7,Fwarning following a fire believed to
OL,8,Fhave been caused by disposable vapes.
OL,10,FMid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService (MAWWFRS) crews were called to
OL,12,Fan incident along the Newtown Bypass
OL,13,Fon Friday, 7 June, as an LGV
OL,14,Fcontaining general recycling waste was
OL,15,Fsmouldering in areas with high
OL,16,Ftemperature readings.
