OL,3,CWarning issued after fire caused by
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes in lorry
OL,6,FAround 30 tonnes of mixed recycling
OL,7,Fhad to be removed from the vehicle
OL,8,Fafter crews gained access to dampen it
OL,9,Fdown. The road was closed due to the
OL,10,Fvehicle's contents spreading onto the
OL,11,Fbypass.
OL,13,FThe fire is believed to have been
OL,14,Fcaused by disposable vapes which had
OL,15,Fnot been correctly disposed of.
OL,17,FSeveral disposable vapes were found in
OL,18,Fthe lorry's contents, which seemed to
OL,19,Fhave been crushed and damaged.
