OL,3,CWarning issued after fire caused by
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes in lorry
OL,6,FThe fire service said this would have
OL,7,Fsparked and ignited the rest of the
OL,8,Frubbish within the lorry.
OL,10,FThree hose reel jets, one thermal
OL,11,Fimaging camera and small gear were
OL,12,Fused to remove the waste and
OL,13,Fextinguish the fire.
OL,15,FThis incident required a multi-agency
OL,16,Fresponse with Natural Resources Wales,
OL,17,FDyfed-Powys Police and the local
OL,18,Fauthority in attendance. Crews left
OL,19,Fthe scene at 12:27am on Saturday, 8
OL,20,FJune.
