OL,3,CWarning issued after fire caused by
OL,4,Cdisposable vapes in lorry
OL,6,F"Lithium-ion batteries are hidden
OL,7,Finside many everyday household
OL,8,Felectricals, from laptops, mobile
OL,9,Fphones and tablets to electric
OL,10,Ftoothbrushes, vapes and earpods.
OL,12,F"These batteries can become crushed or
OL,13,Fdamaged in bin lorries or waste sites
OL,14,Fif they aren't recycled and can lead
OL,15,Fto a fire.
OL,17,F"Not only do battery fires endanger
OL,18,Flives, but they can also cause serious
OL,19,Fenvironmental and health risks."
